11) Create "Cost per claim & YoY by Site" Chart. 18

Now It become easy to built a chart based on another one. this chart it pretty similar than the previous one, lets do it.

  1. Copy  and past "Cost per claim & YoY by Type" Chart.   Use Ctrl V  to past  the chart.
  2. Delete the "Claim type"  From the shared axis .
  3. Drag and drop "Claim Site" column to the shared axis.
  4. Click on format visual
  5. Go to title and open it 
  6. Change the title from "Cost per claim & YoY by Type" to  "Cost per claim & YoY by Site"
  7. You should get a chart like this chart bellow.



           

There are more ways to copy and past in power Bi, see the video bellow:
